Multnomah County Circuit Court

040343610; A127636 174 P3d 1094 Peter Ozanne, Executive Director, Peter Gartlan, Chief Defender, Legal Services Division, and Stephanie Hortsch, Deputy Public Defender, Office of Public Defense Services, filed the briefs for appellant.
